1330|title=Eus\u00e9bio: Governo decreta tr\u00eas dias de luto nacional|date=Jan 5, 2014|work=[[A Bola]]}}</ref>\n*[[Ferenc Pusk\u00e1s]] (Hungary)\n*[[Ayrton Senna]] (Brazil)\n\n===Cultural figures===\n*[[Israel Kamakawiwo\u02bbole]] (Hawaii)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://archives.starbulletin.com/1997/07/10/news/story3.html|title=Honolulu Star-Bulletin Local News|website=archives.starbulletin.com}}</ref>\n*[[Am\u00e1lia Rodrigues]] (Portugal)<ref>{{cite web |url= https://web.archive.org/web/20010304192704/http://www.attambur.com/Noticias/Amalia/desaparecimentoamalia.htm|title=Bio |website= www.attambur.com|access-date=2020-01-09}}</ref>\n*[[To\u0161e Proeski]] (North Macedonia)\n*[[Chinghiz Aitmatov]] (Kyrgyzstan)\n*[[Charles Aznavour]] (Armenia)\n*[[Mihai Volontir]] (Moldova)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ru.publika.md/17-sentyabrya-obyavili-dnem-nacionalnogo-traura-strana-prostitsya-s-mikhaem-volontirom_1701081.html|title=17 \u0441\u0435\u043d\u0442\u044f\u0431\u0440\u044f \u043e\u0431\u044a\u044f\u0432\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0434\u043d\u0435\u043c \u043d\u0430\u0446\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0442\u0440\u0430\u0443\u0440\u0430: \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430 \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0442\u0441\u044f \u0441 \u041c\u0438\u0445\u0430\u0435\u043c \u0412\u043e\u043b\u043e\u043d\u0442\u0438\u0440\u043e\u043c &#124; PUBLIKA .MD - AICI SUNT \u0218TIRILE|first=PUBLIKA MD-AICI SUNT|last=\u0218TIRILE|date=September 15, 2015|website=ru.publika.md}}</ref>\n*[[Karel Gott]] (Czech Republic)\n\n===Tragedies===\n*Victims of [[Hurricane Hazel]] ([[Haiti]], 3 days)\n*Victims of the [[Great Chilean earthquake]] of 1960.\n*Victims of the 1990 20 January [[Black January]] [[Massacre]] by [[Soviet Union]]'s [[Red army]] ([[Azerbaijan]], [[Baku]])\n*Victims of the [[1996 Kamianske tram accident]] ([[Ukraine]], July 3, 1996)<ref name=\"Maharishi Institute\">{{cite web|last1=Kolomayets|first1=Marta|title=Ukraine mourns tram accident victims|u